did.unittitle: School of Management, Yale University, records

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of administrative files, grade reports, admission files, a survey, registrar notebooks, financial aid records, and committee files documenting the establishment of and search for a dean of the Yale School of Organization and Management (known as the School of Management after 1995).

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 30-A (YRG 30-A), Central records and records of the dean of the Yale School of Management.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: While this collection as a whole is available for research, parts of it may be restricted due to law, university policy or fragility. Any restricted material will be noted as such.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: School of Management, Yale University, Records (RU 486). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of administrative files, grade reports, admission files, a survey, registrar notebooks, financial aid records, and committee files documenting the establishment of and search for a dean of the Yale School of Organization and Management (known as the School of Management after 1995) as well as the records of Professor Clayton P. Alderfer, former Director of Professional Studies.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The Registrar's notebooks consist academic calendars, course information and schedules, enrollment and tuition data, class/student lists (including non-SOM students), grade and degree requirements, diploma lists, and commencement records. Additional records are listed below in notes with the individual notebooks.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The Registrar's notebooks are arranged chonologically by academic year (Fall-Spring).

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Also includes exam schedules, course preference questionnaires, and Outside and Special student reports.
